Bokasi bonene bwa '''basindika''' nde [[lisangá]]. Soko basali bazali motema moko mpe bakosalisana solo, soko baboyi [[avoka]] mpé [[madesu ya bana]]; wana ndebakoki kobatela makoki ma bango, wana ndebakoki kosengisa [[patro|bapatro]] na mpé [[leta]] bapesa basali maye masengeli na bango. 

